## 🔧 开发

```bash
$ corepack enable

$ git clone https://github.com/marchen-dev/marchen-player.git

$ pnpm install

$ cp .env.example .env

$ pnpm dev
```

## 📎 技术栈

- Electron
- React
- TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS
- Jotai
- shadcn/ui
- TanStack Query
- Framer motion
- xgplayer

